# Client-side
<client>
<server>
http
</server>
<features>
NTLM
</features>
 <name>
HTTP proxy-auth NTLM and then POST
 </name>
 <command>
http://%HOSTIP:%HTTPPORT/239 --proxy http://%HOSTIP:%HTTPPORT --proxy-user silly:person --proxy-ntlm -d "postit"
</command>
</client>

